---
import Slide from '@decks/templates/Slide.astro';

import priorArt from '../images/anvil-prior-art.png?url';
---

<Slide title="Anvil" subtitle="Context">
	<div
		class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] items-center gap-12"
	>
		<ul class="flex list-none flex-col gap-4">
			<li class="text-subdued text-3xl leading-snug">
				ServiceTitan’s apps had no shared system. No
				consistency, no alignment, no process for change
				across teams.
			</li>
			<li class="text-subdued text-3xl leading-snug">
				I had to build the design system on a live, shipping
				product. The train while riding it.
			</li>
			<li class="text-subdued text-3xl leading-snug">
				Started with 13 interviews across design, eng, PM, and
				beyond to find what actually needed standardizing.
			</li>
		</ul>
		<img
			src={priorArt}
			alt="Audit of existing styles, components, and color palettes across ServiceTitan products"
			class="m-0! block max-h-none! w-[900px] max-w-none! rounded-2xl"
		/>
	</div>
</Slide>
